headline: How Investors Are Reacting To Realty Income (O) Expanding Into Global Logistics With GIC Partnership
summary: Realty Income recently expanded its international footprint by forming a partnership with Singapore’s GIC to commit over US$1.50 billion to build-to-suit logistics real estate and completing its first investment in Mexico, further diversifying its property portfolio.
